::Zardus/Ramulus::

Zardus turns around, looking at Gotron. He raises an eyebrow. Lots of bots 
have been joining lately...

"You too? Allright, follow me," he says, "I'll assign you quarters."

Ordering the external defences to let Gotron through, Zardus walks back into 
the base, heading for the residential area.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Ramulus follows Brix and Fliq, carrying an armload of computer equipment.

"Yeah, I died once," he says, answering Fliq's earlier question, "A Predacon 
attack on the Ark."

His eyes narrow, remembering the experience. "I don't recommend dying, its 
not too fun."
